physdesc.extent: 54 containers: 53 letter document boxes, 1 legal document box

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Open for research. Researchers interested in accessing digital media (floppy disks, CDs, DVDs, etc.) in this collection must use an access surrogate. The original items may not be accessed because of preservation concerns. Access copy currently unavailable. Please contact a RAC archivist for further instruction.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The Henry Luce Foundation records (Record Group 11) consists primarily of grant files.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: RAC holds legal title. The Henry Luce Foundation retains all applicable intellectual property rights in so far as it holds them.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The Henry Luce Foundation records (Record Group 11) are arranged as received.
